Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:43.56,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pay Back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:44.73,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}今日も労働
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:46.19,Jigoku_OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}One verse One punch
